videos.headline: LSU advances to SEC semis with a big win over Georgia
videos.description: LSU gets a big game from Alexis Morris as they advance to the semifinals of the SEC tournament with a 83-66 win over Georgia.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (LSU advances to SEC semis with a big win over Georgia) 2023/03/03 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LSU's Morris, Reese share the love after beating UGA
videos.description: Following an 83-66 win vs. the 7-seed Bulldogs, Alexis Morris (28 points) and Angel Reese (15 points) praise one another for the 2-seed Tigers' victory.

videos.headline: Georgia, LSU are delayed in 2nd quarter after roof leak
videos.description: Georgia and LSU have a 44-minute delay as a storm causes some water to fall on the court.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Misc. (Georgia, LSU are delayed in 2nd quarter after roof leak) 2023/03/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU's Johnson speaks on her mindset and the 'big three'
videos.description: Flau'jae Johnson describes how herself, Angel Reese and Alexis Morris mesh together to produce for the Tigers against UGA.

videos.headline: Morris, LSU's 3-pointers lead takedown of UGA
videos.description: The 2-seed Tigers drain 11 from behind the arc as Alexis Morris scores a game-high 28 points in the 83-66 rout of the 7-seed Bulldogs in the quarterfinals.
